  • 方法详细资料

    • containsRelationType

      boolean containsRelationType​(String name)
      Checks whether a type with the specified name exists.
      参数:
      name - name of the type
      返回:
      true, if a type with the given name exists, else false

    • getRelationType

      RelationType getRelationType​(String name)
      Returns the type with the given name. Note, that type names must be unique.
      参数:
      name - name of the type to return
      返回:
      The type with the given name, or null if such does not exist
      另请参阅:
      RelationType

    • containsPropertyKey

      boolean containsPropertyKey​(String name)
      Checks whether a property key of the given name has been defined in the JanusGraph schema.
      参数:
      name - name of the property key
      返回:
      true, if the property key exists, else false

    • getOrCreatePropertyKey

      PropertyKey getOrCreatePropertyKey​(String name)
      Returns the property key with the given name. If automatic type making is enabled, it will make the property key using the configured default type maker if a key with the given name does not exist.
      参数:
      name - name of the property key to return
      返回:
      the property key with the given name
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if a property key with the given name does not exist or if the type with the given name is not a property key
      另请参阅:
      PropertyKey

    • getOrCreatePropertyKey

      default PropertyKey getOrCreatePropertyKey​(String name, Object value)
      Returns the property key with the given name. If automatic type making is enabled, it will make the property key using the configured default type maker if a key with the given name does not exist. The default implementation simply calls the getOrCreatePropertyKey method
      参数:
      name - name of the property key to return
      value - the value of the property key. This param is not used by the default implementation
      返回:
      the property key with the given name
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if a property key with the given name does not exist or if the type with the given name is not a property key
      另请参阅:
      PropertyKey

    • getOrCreatePropertyKey

      default PropertyKey getOrCreatePropertyKey​(String name, Object value, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.VertexProperty.Cardinality cardinality)
      Returns the property key with the given name. If automatic type making is enabled, it will make the property key using the configured default type maker if a key with the given name does not exist. If automatic type making is enabled, it will make the property key using the selected cardinality, if a key with the given name does not exist. The default implementation simply calls the getOrCreatePropertyKey method
      参数:
      name - name of the property key to return
      value - the value of the property key. This param is not used by the default
      cardinality - the cardinality of the property key. This param is not used by the default implementation
      返回:
      the property key with the given name
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if a property key with the given name does not exist or if the type with the given name is not a property key
      另请参阅:
      PropertyKey

    • getPropertyKey

      PropertyKey getPropertyKey​(String name)
      Returns the property key with the given name. If it does not exist, NULL is returned
      参数:
      name -
      返回:

      boolean containsEdgeLabel​(String name)

      参数:
      name - name of the edge label
      返回:
      true, if the edge label exists, else false

    • getOrCreateEdgeLabel

      EdgeLabel getOrCreateEdgeLabel​(String name)
      Returns the edge label with the given name. If automatic type making is enabled, it will make the edge label using the configured default type maker if a label with the given name does not exist.
      参数:
      name - name of the edge label to return
      返回:
      the edge label with the given name
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if an edge label with the given name does not exist or if the type with the given name is not an edge label
      另请参阅:
      EdgeLabel

    • getEdgeLabel

      返回:

    • getOrCreateVertexLabel

      VertexLabel getOrCreateVertexLabel​(String name)
      Returns the vertex label with the given name. If a vertex label with this name does not exist, the label is automatically created through the registered DefaultSchemaMaker.

      Attempting to automatically create a vertex label might cause an exception depending on the configuration.

      参数:
      name -
      返回:
